# Arquivo de testes HTTP para a API
# Use a extensão REST Client no VS Code para executar

### Variáveis
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001/api/v1
@token = seu_token_aqui

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:3001/health

### ========================================
### AUTENTICAÇÃO
### ========================================

### Login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@example.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

### Obter usuário autenticado
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/logout
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### ========================================
### BITDEFENDER
### ========================================

### Listar todas as licenças
GET {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Obter licença específica
GET {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Criar nova licença (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "company": "Empresa Teste",
  "contactPerson": "João Silva",
  "email": "joao@empresa.com",
  "licenseKey": "TEST-KEY-123",
  "totalLicenses": 50,
  "expirationDate": "2027-12-31",
  "renewalStatus": "Ativo",
  "notes": "Licença de teste"
}

### Atualizar licença (Admin)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "totalLicenses": 60,
  "renewalStatus": "Renovado",
  "usedSlots": 45,
  "totalSlots": 60
}

### Deletar licença (Admin)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Deletar múltiplas licenças (Admin)
POST {{baseUrl}}/bitdefender/bulk-delete
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ids": [1, 2, 3]
}
